        <p class="normal-text sml">A combination of LinkedIn, CrowdCompass, Twitter, and SurveyMonkey. API serves data to web, iOS, and Android applications. Features: Multilingual, Multitenant, Versioned, Secure, RESTful.</p>
        <p class="normal-text sml"><strong>Using Evanta365 an event attendee can:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li class="normal-text sml">View event agenda and add sessions to their schedule</li>
          <li class="normal-text sml">Connect with other attendees (similar to FaceBook friending or following on Twitter)</li>
          <li class="normal-text sml">See speakers, their bios, ask questions</li>
          <li class="normal-text sml">Join or create groups of like-minded attendees</li>
          <li class="normal-text sml">Participate in discussions, like posts, add comments, send private messages</li>
          <li class="normal-text sml">Enter drawings for luxury prizes provided by event sponsors</li>
          <li class="normal-text sml">Take part in the Leaderboard which awards points for various in-app activities (gamification)</li>
          <li class="normal-text sml">Complete evaluations and surveys</li>
        </ul>
        </div>
